Title: Grammar Based Information Modelling  Grammar Based Information Modelling.  
Author: A.H.M. ter Hofstede and H.A. Proper ; and Th.P. van der Weide A.H.M. ter Hofstede, H.A. Proper, and Th.P. van der Weide. 
